name: Tango | Gen 11 Brisk Skyblue
bio: Hi-ya! I'm Tango | Gen 11 Brisk Skyblue. I enjoy shakin' dat booty, glaring at the neighbour's cat, and watching Stranger Things. I once dreamed of being a Aerobics Athlete . Now I can be found braiding people's hair all day. Maybe you and I can be partners in crime.
